The paper discusses the use of Ensemble Decision Systems for General Video Game Playing, which involves artificial intelligence, machine learning, and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of game theory in decision making makes cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) a possible category. The paper also mentions the use of computer vision techniques, which makes cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) another possible category. Finally, the paper discusses the performance analysis of the Ensemble Decision System, which involves control systems and optimization, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category as well.
